snippet.textDisplay: To All those comparing qawali styles .qawali  varies from family to family . Also is a very experimentle form of music . Nusrat saabs father  completly changed the face of  qawali  when he  was a part of it .. and nusrat  saab was always experimenting . Sabri household is different  .. aziz mian is different .. etc etc .. we cannot compare and say this is authentic  or that is authentic  when qawali is about improvisation and experimentation  . But one thing in common love for The Creator and his beloveds  , peace and harmony.
